title: Jasmin Hurić
text:
Jasmin Hurić (born 14 September 1972) is a former Bosnian-Herzegovinian international <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
International career.
He made his debut for <a href="Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina%20national%20football%20team">Bosnia and Herzegovina</a> in a June 2001 <a href="friendly%20match">friendly match</a> against <a href="Slovakia%20national%20football%20team">Slovakia</a> and has earned a total of 8 caps (2 unofficial), scoring no goals. His final international was an October 2002 <a href="UEFA%20Euro%202004%20qualifying">European Championship qualification</a> match against <a href="Norway%20national%20football%20team">Norway</a>.
